basisset.dc:description: Partridge Uncontracted Basis Sets --------------------------------- Elements Reference Li, Be: (18s) H. Partridge, J. Chem. Phys. 90, 1043 (1989). B - Ne: (18s,13p) Na - Mg: (25s,16p) H. Partridge, J. Chem. Phys. 87, 6643 (1987). K : (20s,12p) Ca : (23s,16p) Sc - V : (23s,16p,8d) Cr Mn: (23s,15p,11d) Fe - Co: (23s,16p,8d) Ni : (23s,16p,10d) Cu : (23s,15p,8d) Zn : (23s,16p,8d) These are groundstate, RHF energy-optimized, uncontracted basis sets. This set is one of the smaller sets of uncontracted, energy-optimized primitives published by H. Partridge. The MSRC basis set library contains small, intermediate and large Partridge basis sets.
